This is a modified version of Martin Kaltenbrunner's TuioKinect (http://code.google.com/p/tuiokinect/). It uses Haar face-detection to automatically set the hand-detection threshold.

You will need openFrameworks (github version, untested with 062) and the following addons:

ofxVectorMath
ofxThred
ofxOsc
ofxOpenCv
ofxKinect

optionally, for GUI:

ofxXmlSettings
ofxMSAInteractiveObject
ofxSimpleGuiToo

Tested and compiled with Xcode, OSX 10.6.